data.description: Close to ISU!! 4 bedrooms, 1 bath, livinging room with large picture windows, den, the basement room could be used as a bedroom or family room, lots of storage and built ins, stove, fridge, washer and dryer stay with the home, plus newer windows! Gas heat and central air conditioning. Covered patio to enjoy all the flowers that are coming up in the spring along with the possibility of having a pond or fountain, 2 sheds, could be your perfect flower garden oasis. Call listing agent today for your private showing.
